title: Molina Drops After 2026 Profit Forecast Misses Expectations
description: Molina Healthcare Inc. plunged 33% after the health insurer forecast 2026 profit that was less than half of Wall Street’s expectations and said it would stop offering Medicare Advantage prescription drug plans for 2027 as medical costs increased across all of its major programs.
